snippet.title: WRC 9 | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Thrust into the heart of the new WRC Season with WRC 9, the first game in the series coming to Xbox Series X and PlayStation 5! 

#WRC9 will release on September 3 on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, Epic Games Store, and at a later date on Xbox Series X and PlayStation and Nintendo Switch. 

-------------------------------
